tracked_keywords.tooltipText: Total count of tracked keywords for this product

amazon_choice_count.tooltipText: Total count of keyword results based on the Amazon Choice badge status

search_volume.tooltipText: Estimated total count the keyword(s) is searched monthly on Amazon

organic.tooltipText: Organic search position result from using that keyword(s)

sponsored.tooltipText: Total count of ASINs running sponsored ads from using that keyword(s)

true_rank_performance.tooltipText: Percentage of product ranking changes over a period of time, in order to see the real impact of ranking changes on product sales

search_volume.tooltipText: Estimated total count the tracked keyword(s) is searched monthly on Amazon

competing_products.tooltipText: Total count of product showed in customer searches from using the tracked keyword(s)

position_rank.tooltipText: Organic search position result from using the tracked keyword(s)

relative_rank.tooltipText: Rank of the main ASIN relative it its competitors. For example, if three (3) competitors are ranked better than the main ASIN the relative rank will be four (4)

rank_average.tooltipText: Average position detected compared to all products

ranking_asins.tooltipText: Average position detected compared to all products

sponsored_rank.tooltipText: Sponsored ads position in customer searches

drop_raise_index.tooltipText: Percentage of weighted drop/ raise of the tracked keyword compared to previous value
